-- Definición de las IAs --
Estructuras que puedo usar:
PASS    
STANDARD_ACTION
MOVE_ACTION
MOVE_ACTION - STANDARD_ACTION
STANDARD_ACTION - MOVE_ACTION
MOVE_ACTION - MOVE_ACTION
FULL_ACTION

STANDARD_ACTION: Attack TARGET
                 // Cast X Spell TARGET
                 
MOVE_ACTION: // Random
             - Approach (TARGET) ?
             // Disengage
             // Defend
             // Flank (TARGET) ?

FULL_ACTION: // Retreat
             - Full attack TARGET
             // Charge (TARGET)
     
TARGET: - ADJECTIVE ally
        - ADJECTIVE enemy
        - Self
        - Specific Character
        
ADJECTIVES: - Closest / Furthest
            - Most injured / Least injured
            // Random (Random available?)
            - Last
            // Best / Worst specific stat (If available)
            // Most / Least vulnerable to spell? (If available)
// Posiblemente alguno más aprovechando las cosas de las conditions
// Ver de agregar condiciones de estilo true/false para decidir cosas (Por ejemplo, closest in sight)

// RANDOM_CHOICE [accion]
// TRY accion, accion, accion, ..., DEFAULT accion
IF condicion THEN accion ELSE accion
ACCION ; ACCION
WHILE condicion do ACCION

CONDICIONES: - Team count COMPARISON Int
             - Team : Unit count COMPARISON Int
             // Team : Unit : ID stat COMPARISON Something
             - Team : Unit in RANGE
             // Specific Unit Threat Count COMPARISON Int
             - TARGET in RANGE
             // Team Unit Count in RANGE COMPARISON Int
             // Specific Unit in specific place?
             // Specific unit alive?
             // Relative Turn Count?
             - total turn count COMPARISON Int
             
             - Not CONDICION
             - CONDICION and CONDICION
             - CONDICION or CONDICION
             - (CONDICION)
             
RANGE: - INT
       - Melee
       - Ranged attack range
       - Speed
       - RANGE + RANGE
       - RANGE * RANGE




Default actions when the action is not possible:

Attack -> Target not in range: Approach Target
          Invalid target: Look for closest target / previous target
Cast X Spell -> Target not in range: Approach Target
                Invalid target: Look for closest target / previous target of the same team
                Not anymore charges: Skip the turn
Random -> Not able to move: Defend
Approach Target -> Invalid target: Look for closest target / previous target / most relevant target
                   Not able to move: Defend
Flank Target -> Target not in range: Keep Approaching
                Not able to move: Defend
Disengage -> Not able to move: Defend
Retreat -> Not able to move: Defend
Charge Target -> Target not in range: Approach Target
                 Invalid target: Look for closest target / previous target / available target
Full attack Target -> Target not in range: Charge Target / Approach target
                      Invalid target: Look for closest target / previous target / available target                 
